imp is declared in the proxy.
Vault._delegate().imp (../../smart-contract-sanctuary/bsc/contracts/mainnet/proxies/0.8.0/35b3edE207A73575F0e69369e90F07d9D259AfD1_Vault.sol/35b3edE207A73575F0e69369e90F07d9D259AfD1_Vault.sol#22) gets value from a cross-contract call: IPool(pool).vaultImplementation()

Could not find setter for pool
Missing compatibility check in Vault.fallback()
